{"tid":521264,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[估國家] 羽絨離奇爆炸","createTime":"2018-01-06T11:13:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-06T16:00:53.000Z","uid":37,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"01874fe360ba95e03d2101bec33e4cca64c60578","tid":521264,"uid":37,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:13:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180106/57673588\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57673588&d=Jfrr3VwRFbLVwLPZ0c4nXDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=7ba1e47e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180106%2F57673588&h=4c2a9983\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180106/57673588</a><br />\n每逢冬天，許多人都會穿上羽絨保暖。但日前，浙江麗水發生一宗罕見意外，一名婦人身上的羽絨離奇爆炸，羽絨被爆出幾個穿孔，幸好老伯沒有大礙。<br />\n<br />\n事發於前日上午，張姓老伯在家中，與妻子收拾行李準備回鄉。妻子當時在廚房收拾的雜物，突然「嘭」的一聲，身上的羽絨突然爆炸。張伯初時以為是煤氣爆炸，但見妻子萬分驚惶從廚房走出來。<br />\n<br />\n張大爺指，自己只是用膠袋將電飯鍋包着，其他都沒有做過，走出廚房前，一切都正常。事發後，除了妻子羽絨被炸穿，煤氣罐邊上的毛巾和垃圾袋都被灼燒。<br />\n<br />\n附近鄰居表示，事發後，屋內有濃烈煤氣味，更發現煤氣罐有疑似氣體洩漏，當時即時扭緊氣罐上的氣閥。為安全起見，更將煤氣罐煤搬往露台。<br />\n<br />\n當地消防表示，可能是因為煤氣洩露達到一定的濃度，羽絨產生靜電，令羽絨發生爆炸。由於冬天天氣比較乾燥，許多衣物會產生靜電，或引發煤氣爆炸，故市民使用完煤氣一定要及時關上。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515225566_18a5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F1515225566_18a5.png&h=055bfc0a&s={SIZE}\" /><a href=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515225566_18a5.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180106%2Flarge%2F1515225566_18a5.png&d=Jfrr3VwRFbLVwLPZ0c4nXDPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=620d7f75\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180106/large/1515225566_18a5.png</a>"},{"pid":"fb86c354b30f5cf19f895fdbaf90020a6e424d8f","tid":521264,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:16:17.000Z","msg":"又係天水圍"},{"pid":"e0a986854aeda015556149d0e5846ec597c87c58","tid":521264,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T11:21:45.000Z","msg":"卡通片咩 羽絨都會爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e3f49b9ccf13c7548d5e6fa0d6d20d4373295ed","tid":521264,"uid":37,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T12:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b15efd80be64b2615fe8dba23b685fa79a4d34f9","tid":521264,"uid":110620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T16:00:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}